    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered since day one. The paint is flawless, the interior still has that new car smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make someone very happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
