      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for it to find a new home. Honestly, it's in stunning condition\u2014it still has that fresh feel and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this beauty since day one, so it drives perfectly and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new, you've gotta come check this one out. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
