    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of high-revving atmospheric engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from a preventative rear subframe reinforcement and fresh polyurethane bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. Power is managed via the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and corner-exit traction. Every factory body panel retains its original depth and luster, with zero evidence of thermal fatigue on the cooling system or oxidation on the undercarriage. This is a reference-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
